    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong><i>Beyond the Struggle</i></strong>, players will face various challenges that are common in modern life. Use your strategic thinking to manage stress, overcome obstacles, and rise to life's challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras/c5bf1ca176b2335425b01e9875cdde16.avif?t=1737998600\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras_big/c5bf1ca176b2335425b01e9875cdde16.avif?t=1737998600 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Building Strategy Cards</strong>�</u><br>Drag recipe cards to the table, add resources, and craft strategy cards. These cards represent your inner strategies, helping you manage resources and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Build carefully to shape your path.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras/b6c8920da908e4227eec92b2d1a7fc13.avif?t=1737998600\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Resource Management</strong>�</u><br>Strategy cards generate action points and emotional energy, while challenges reward knowledge reserves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Balance building and overcoming challenges to thrive.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras/9ccc7490e283ede3cc890dfc85d15d31.avif?t=1737998600\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Handling Challenge Cards</strong>�</u><br>Challenge cards reflect the struggles you face in life. Resolve them within the time limit to avoid increased pressure or new setbacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Adapt, persist, and rise above!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras/87f93400bb951dc6b76e3585da3caf6b.avif?t=1737998600\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Card Building</strong>: Create and customize your card deck to face different life challenges, from stress at work to personal dilemmas, and find the best strategies to manage them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-Life Simulation</strong>: From managing your career to nurturing relationships and taking care of your health, the game immerses you in the ups and downs of real life, testing your ability to juggle multiple aspects of personal well-being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339240/extras/44281853952c92c7b3f0d2739a6d37fb.avif?t=1737998600\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>ENJOY!</u></i></strong></p>",
